Gretchen Hartman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gretchen_Hartman 0 Gretchen Hartman (Chicago, August 28, 1897 – Los Angeles, January 27, 1979) was an American stage and film actress. She is credited on 67 movies, nearly all silent, but is perhaps better known as the wife of actor Alan Hale Sr., and mother of actor Alan Hale Jr..
